snippet.title: Larry Lawton
snippet.description:
BIO:  Larry Lawton is the Author of Gangster Redemption, TV Personality, Speaker, Prison Expert & Law Enforcement Consultant. Larry developed the nationally recognized Reality Check Program to help young people make better choices and connect Law Enforcement with the community. 

Larry Lawton is the only ex-con in the US to be sworn in as an Honorary Police Officer and only ex-con to be recognized on the Floor of the United States Congress for helping young people, families and LE.

Business/Collab: business@larrylawtonjewelthief.com
